text: Leninskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Iglino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Leninskoye, Kaltovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
